IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
SSLType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
User eddie.hickey@rivethealth.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.gnupg/google.gpg"

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/
Inbox ~/.mail/

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns "[Gmail]/Spam" "[Gmail]/Trash" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
